  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>As a part of this jutsu, you impale yourself with your weapon, coating it in your blood, reduce your current hit die to 0, and you take 4d12 necrotic damage to yourself that cannot be reduced in any way.</p><p>You cannot lose concentration on this jutsu as a result of damage.</p><p>As a result, your weapon becomes a living embodiment of your lifeforce extending in range and enhancing its lethality. For the duration your weapon's range is doubled, deals +4d12 necrotic damage twice per turn, ignores resistances and immunity, and deals double damage to structures and constructs.</p>",
